VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'bad news, but uh rather some things you should know. So, the good news is that the install itself is probably the easiest uh open-source installation you\'ll ever run across. Uh just simply, you know, choose your OS, uh hit the button, and then, you know, the download'

[02:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'happens. So, that\'s just the installer part. Just as an FYI. From there, of course, is where the actual install begins. It will start downloading models, and I do want to note, it\'s a pretty beefy boy. Uh depending on what you already have installed, like Python,'

[03:03] [scene:talk]
