VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'in here, hit save key, and now, uh, essentially, your text encoder is running through the LTX API. Um, it doesn\'t cost you anything, so that I mean, save yourself 25 gigs if you want to and just do it this way. Now, for'

[04:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'kind of the elephant in the room, and it is a pretty heavy elephant, uh, LTX desktop currently hard gates local generation at 32 gigs of VRAM. So, on the consumer side, uh, there\'s actually'

