AUDIO: 'only one GPU that has 32 gigs of VRAM, and that\'s the RTX 5090. If you don\'t have a 5090, uh, don\'t stress about it too much. This probably is not going to last very long and actually has been already solved, as we\'ll see in just a'

[04:55] [scene:talk]
